 g ripe tomatoes, cut into quarters","1 tsp salt, plus extra for sprinkling","5 sprigs fresh parsley, leaves only","5 sprigs fresh mint, leaves only","1 tsp ground cumin","½ tsp ground cayenne pepper, adjust to taste","1 tsp ground cinnamon","1 tsp ground paprika","1 tsp ground allspice","½ tsp dried chilli flakes, adjust to taste","2 tbsp pomegranate molasses","500 g lamb mince"]},{"title":"Assembly and baking","content":["30 g pine nuts","2 lemons, cut into quarters"]}],"id":"r168171","imageLink":"https:\/\/3.bp.blogspot.com\/-dPc-ZTByENE\/XZanjoWZTHI\/AAAAAAAAhAw\/Qe-r82U9GigWV5EiPlVm7bZXe4hYqmmPACLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_MRNIygTd9v1ar4_C.png","title":"Spiced lamb flatbread","publishedAt":"2018-10-15T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"26.6 g","fat":"14 g","uom":"per 1 piece","carbohydrates":"52.6 g","calories":"1853 kJ \/ 443 kcal"},"usefulItems":"cling film, baking tray or baking stone, rolling pin, baking tray, oven","hintsAndTricks":["Accompany with salad and a savoury yogurt drink, garnished with fresh chopped mint and parsley leaves."],"basicInfo":["medium","30m","1h 50m","6 pieces"]}